These are Puzzles for 2x5 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-1::.
There are 5 different nationalities: malaysian, indonesian, mexican, nigerian, french
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: dubstep, indie, jazz, pop, soul
1. the fan of pop is on the left of the nigerian##1
2. the french is on the right of the malaysian##1
3. the fan of pop is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
4. the indonesian is on the far left##1
5. the fan of soul is on the far left##1
6. the malaysian is in the middle##1
7. the fan of soul is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4     |   5    |
| Nationality   | indonesian | mexican | malaysian | french | nigerian |
| Music-Genre   | soul    | dubstep | jazz     | pop       | indie  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-2::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, fanta, soy-milk, sprite
5 different pets are kept: horse, frog, goat, turtle, ferret
1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
4. the person drinking almond-milk is in the middle##1
5. the person drinking coffee is the owner of the goat##1
6. the owner of the ferret is the person drinking sprite##1
7. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |      3      |    4     |   5    |
| Beverage      | coffee | fanta | almond-milk | soy-milk | sprite |
| Pet   | goat  | turtle   | horse       | frog    | ferret   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-3::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, fonseca, dannemann, game, dunhill
The people use 5 different means of transport: boat, bus, jet-ski, ship, subway
1. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
2. the game-smoker is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
3. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
4. the dannemann-smoker is on the far left##1
5. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
6. the fonseca-smoker is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |     2     |   3    |    4    |     5     |
| Cigar        | dannemann | game | fonseca | tiparillo | dunhill |
| Transport   | bus  | boat      | subway | jet-ski | ship      |

