.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-4::.
There 5 different types of food: grapes, spinach, grapefruit, pepper, watermelon
The people have 5 different jobs:  fisherman, nurse, paramedic, social-worker, writer
1. the person eating watermelon is on the right of the nurse##1
2. the person eating grapefruit is on the left of the nurse##1
3. the social-worker is on the right of the fisherman##1
4. the person eating spinach is on the right of the writer##1
5. the person eating grapes is on the left of the person eating grapefruit##1
6. the paramedic is on the far right##1
7. the writer is on the right of the person eating grapes##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |    3    |    4    |     5     |
| Food   | pepper    | grapes        | grapefruit | spinach | watermelon |
| Job     | fisherman | social-worker | writer  | nurse   | paramedic |

