.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-5::.
There 5 different types of food: banana, cherry, grapes, mango, strawberry
There are 5 different nationalities: dutch, nigerian, italian, mexican, malaysian
1. the mexican is on the right of the person eating grapes##1
2. the nigerian is the person eating strawberry##1
3. the italian is on the left of the person eating mango##1
4. the italian is in the middle##1
5. the person eating grapes is on the left of the person eating banana##1
6. the malaysian is the person eating mango##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |    3     |       4       |     5      |
| Food    | grapes   | banana     | cherry   | mango         | strawberry |
| Nationality   | dutch | mexican | italian | malaysian | nigerian     |

