.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-6::.
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: disco, metal, techno, pop, jazz
The people use 5 different means of transport: car, helicopter, quad-bike, roller, skateboard
1. the person driving the roller is in the middle##1
2. the person driving the car is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
4. the person driving the quad-bike is the fan of techno##1
5. the fan of jazz is on the right of the fan of metal##1
6. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the fan of disco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |     5     |
| Music-Genre       | pop   | techno   | metal | jazz | disco |
| Transport   | helicopter | quad-bike | roller   | skateboard | car       |

