.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-7::.
5 different pets are kept: chinchilla, frog, pony, rabbit, rat
There are 5 different nationalities: german, chinese, japanese, nigerian, thai
1. the owner of the pony is on the right of the nigerian##1
2. the german is the owner of the chinchilla##1
3. the owner of the rat is on the right of the japanese##1
4. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
5. the chinese is in the middle##1
6. the japanese is the owner of the pony##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |   2   |    3     |     4      |     5      |
| Pet     | frog   | pony  | rat      | chinchilla | rabbit     |
| Nationality   | nigerian | japanese | chinese | german   | thai |

