.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-8::.
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: orchid, iris, lily, bellflower, daffodil
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: ice-hockey, rugby, soccer, tennis, water-polo
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1
2. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
3. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
4. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
5. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
6. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
7. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |
| Flower     | iris | orchid       | daffodil | bellflower | lily    |
| Sport   | tennis   | water-polo | soccer  | rugby     | ice-hockey |

