4. the american is on the far left##1
5. the fan of rock is on the left of the fan of classical##1
6. the nigerian is the fan of classical##1
7. the american is on the left of the fan of indie##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |      3       |      4      |    5    |
