.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-12::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: august, november, september, june, february
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: biathlon, cricket, lacrosse, surfing, weightlifting
1. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
2. the person who's birthday is in june is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
3. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
4. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far right##1
5. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
6. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
7. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |    3     |    4    |    5    |
| Birthday    | august | june          | september    | february | november  |
| Sport   | lacrosse  | weightlifting | biathlon | surfing | cricket |

