.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-13::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  chef, freelancer, paramedic, firefighter, designer
The people use 5 different means of transport: bus, snowmobile, subway, train, tram
1. the freelancer is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
2. the person driving the subway is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is the chef##1
4. the designer is the person driving the subway##1
5. the person driving the train is on the left of the chef##1
6. the firefighter is in the middle##1
7. the firefighter is on the right of the chef##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |    3    |    4     |    5    |
| Job   | paramedic | chef      | firefighter | freelancer | designer |
| Transport     | train  | snowmobile | bus     | tram     | subway  |

