4. the indian is the person playing poker##1
5. the person playing domino is on the far right##1
6. the french is on the left of the person playing poker##1
7. the thai is on the left of the person playing whist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |         2          |     3      |   4    |    5     |
| Game           | chess     | monopoly | whist | poker  | domino |
| Nationality   | colombian | thai               | french     | indian | nigerian |

