.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-17::.
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: surfing, swimming, water-polo, tennis, snowboarding
The people use 5 different means of transport: helicopter, jet-ski, scooter, ship, van
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
2. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
3. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
4. the person who's sport is surfing is the person driving the jet-ski##1
5. the person driving the ship is in the middle##1
6. the person who's sport is tennis is the person driving the scooter##1
7. the person who's sport is swimming is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |  3   |    4    |   5    |
| Sport   | surfing   | water-polo    | snowboarding | tennis   | swimming |
| Transport     | jet-ski | helicopter | ship | scooter | van    |

