.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-18::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: action, musical, romance, sports, time-travel
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: august, january, october, november, february
1. the person who's birthday is in november is in the middle##1
2. the person watching action movies is the person who's birthday is in november##1
3. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
4. the person watching time-travel movies is the person who's birthday is in february##1
5. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
6. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
7. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3    |      4      |    5     |
| Movie-Genre   | musical   | sports  | action | time-travel | romance  |
| Birthday         | august | october | november  | february    | january |

