.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-19::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  videographer, social-worker, fisherman, architect, dressmaker
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: basketball, cricket, handball, surfing, tennis
1. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the fisherman##1
2. the architect is on the far right##1
3. the person who's sport is surfing is on the far left##1
4. the person who's sport is handball is the architect##1
5. the videographer is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
6. the social-worker is on the left of the architect##1
7. the videographer is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2      |    3    |   4    |    5     |
| Job   | dressmaker     | fisherman       | videographer     | social-worker  | architect  |
| Sport      | surfing | basketball | cricket | tennis | handball |

