.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-20::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: documentary, drama, romance, satire, thriller
City: paris, hamburg, nizza, miami, liverpool
1. the person traveling to hamburg is in the middle##1
2. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
3. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1
4. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
5. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
6. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2     |    3    |      4      |   5    |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | thriller | romance | documentary | satire |
| City           | liverpool | miami  | hamburg    | paris  | nizza   |

 